dsDescriptionValue.value: Wget provenance data in edge-list format parsed from CamFlow provenance data. This dataset contains benign wget base graph data. Experiments were run for over an hour, with recurrent wget commands issued throughout the experiments (one for every 120 seconds). Background activities were also captured as CamFlow whole-system provenance was turned on. A total of 100 benign experiments and 5 attack one were recorded over a period of 4 days. Provenance data was in JSON format and converted into edge-list format for the Unicorn IDS research project. Conversation time was Sept. 26th, 2018. Each experiment consists of a base and a streaming graph component.
